flowchart TD
  Source[ORISO-UserService repo] --> Maven[./mvnw clean package]
  Maven --> Jar[target/UserService.jar]
  Jar --> Copy[copy to UserService.jar]
  Copy --> Docker[Dockerfile builds image]
  Docker --> K3s[k3s image import]
  K3s --> Rollout[kubectl rollout restart userservice]
  Config[application.properties + env vars] --> Pod[UserService container]
  Rollout --> Pod
